               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 4ra-109va)
                     II) Maṣḥafa lǝdätu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of ʾabuna
                     Takla Haymanot” (fols. 109va-111va)
 - Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols.
                     109va-111va)
 III) Taʾammǝra Takla Hāymānot “Miracles of Takla Haymanot”: 22
                     miracles (fols. 111vb-129rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
<title>Dossier of Takla Haymanot</title>
